Class StudyGroup

java.lang.Object
related_to_the_collection.StudyGroup
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<StudyGroup>
public class StudyGroup extends Object implements Comparable<StudyGroup>
Class representing a study group. This class implements the Comparable interface to allow comparison of study groups based on their unique ID.
